# Knowledge Base Project Structure

This is a full-stack AI-powered knowledge base with persona-driven chat capabilities.

## Main Architecture

- **Frontend**: React + TypeScript in [src/](mdc:src/) directory
- **Backend**: Cloudflare Worker API in [worker/knowledge-base-api/](mdc:worker/knowledge-base-api/)
- **Database**: Cloudflare D1 (SQLite) for personas, knowledge items, chat history
- **AI**: OpenAI GPT-4 integration with comprehensive persona system

